high_descs: Turn around and head straight and left to exit this room, going all the way down the hallway and into the room on the left, approaching the circular diningtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Return to the hallway you came from, go straight and take a left towards the lettuce on the ground.
Cut up the large head of lettuce in the box.
Return to the room where you got the knife and head to the fridge next to the circular table.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Return to the box with the cut up lettuce.
Remove the lettuce from the box.
Return to the room with the fridge and approach the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge, let the lettuce cool down, then remove the lettuce.
Return to the area with the box that you cut the lettuce in and turn right, entering the bathroom.
Place the lettuce on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cut up some lettuce, cool a piece of Lettuce in a fridge and place that Lettuce on a Sink in the bathroom.

Cut the lettuce in the box with the knife.

Put the knife in the fridge.
